        rendering. "fourByFour" samples 1/16 of the pixels per cycle pass. "eightByEight" samples
        1/64 of the pixels per cycle pass. "blueNoise" samples adaptively a number of pixels and splat them to target an objective frame rate.
        """

        allowedTokens = ["noCycling", "deviceOptimal", "fourByFour", "eightByEight", "blueNoise"]
